    # s "I wonder if you qualify for a boy next door, [player_name]..."
    s "じゃあ、[player_name]は私にとってホッとできる男子になれるかな…"

# game/day1.rpy:2106
translate japanese street_sima_ba53245a:

    # p "The only way to tell is for me to keep you company."
    p "それは一緒に付き合ってみないとわからないね"

# game/day1.rpy:2108
translate japanese street_sima_644f7167:

    # s "Sure, why not?"
    s "じゃあ、行こっか？"

# game/day1.rpy:2110
translate japanese street_sima_def4b24b:

    # p "Wow!"
    p "すごい！"

# game/day1.rpy:2111
translate japanese street_sima_fff0a80b:

    # "Somehow, I said it out loud."
    "口に出してしまった"

# game/day1.rpy:2113
translate japanese street_sima_acaf09bb:

    # s "What's so surprising?"
    s "何そんなにびっくりしてるの？"

# game/day1.rpy:2115
translate japanese street_sima_ca20017d:

    # p "Never thought you'd accept..."
    p "受け入れてくれると思わなかったから…"

# game/day1.rpy:2117
translate japanese street_sima_ac2adc83:

    # s "I am curious to hear why, [player_name]."
    s "それはなんでなの、[player_name]？気になる…"

# game/day1.rpy:2119
translate japanese street_sima_1ce33c9d:

    # s "See, now we even have a topic to discuss!"
    s "ほら見て！話内容あるじゃん！"

# game/day1.rpy:2124
translate japanese street_sima_76487acc:

    # "It's evening already. Time sure flies..."
    "わぁ、もう夕方だね。時間経つの早い…"

# game/day1.rpy:2126
translate japanese street_sima_7dd93fe7:

    # s "So? What's so surprising about us walking home together?"
    s "んで、なんで私たちが一緒に帰るの、そんなにびっくりするの？"

# game/day1.rpy:2128
translate japanese street_sima_7afc9222:

    # p "Oh, it's... well..."
    p "まぁ…それは…えーと…"

# game/day1.rpy:2129
translate japanese street_sima_f00d690a:

    # p "Like I told you, I never thought you'd accept."
    p "さっき言ったみたいに、絶対受け入れてくれないと思ったから"

# game/day1.rpy:2131
translate japanese street_sima_ced0b015:

    # p "You seem a bit distant and resorted, that's why..."
    p "それはだって、距離感あるから…"

# game/day1.rpy:2133
translate japanese street_sima_7614373a:

    # s "Hey, that's not true. Maybe it seems like that because of the way I behave..."
    s "それは違うよ。自分の態度でそう思うかもしれないけど…"

# game/day1.rpy:2135
translate japanese street_sima_1058c98d:

    # s "And yes, it takes me some time to open up, but it's only normal."
    s "それに、人にオープンになるのに時間かかるけど、それは普通だよ。"

# game/day1.rpy:2138
translate japanese street_sima_bc408c46:

    # s "I always mind my manners."
    s "いつも自分のマナーを心懸けてる"

# game/day1.rpy:2139
translate japanese street_sima_abe6551c:

    # p "Don't you think it can lead people away?"
    p "でもそうやってて、人々をそらしてない？"

# game/day1.rpy:2141
translate japanese street_sima_94a2cb69:

    # s "Not really... why?"
    s "別に…なんで？"

# game/day1.rpy:2142
translate japanese street_sima_9693b40e:

    # p "Let's say you run into someone who wears the same outfit as you..."
    p "じゃあ、例えば、もしあなたと同じ服を着てる人と通りかかったら？"

# game/day1.rpy:2144
translate japanese street_sima_a988414f:

    # s "Oh my, [player_name], you picked the worst example for a girl."
    s "[player_name]ったら。女の子からしたらひどい例えだね"

# game/day1.rpy:2146
translate japanese street_sima_eba21509:

    # s "In that case, I'd try to cross the street."
    s "その場合、道を渡ろうとするよ"

# game/day1.rpy:2147
translate japanese street_sima_69a6c093:

    # p "I just wanted to say a lot of people won't have enough courage to approach you."
    p "私が言いたかったのは、自信満々であなたに寄ってくる人いないと思う"

# game/day1.rpy:2148
translate japanese street_sima_b29cff7a:

    # p "Who knows, maybe one of them could've became your friend?"
    p "もしかしたら、友達になれたかもしれない"

# game/day1.rpy:2149
translate japanese street_sima_92547822:

    # p "Instead, they would simply think you're not interested."
    p "それどころか、興味ないって思われちゃうよ"

# game/day1.rpy:2151
translate japanese street_sima_d60c6653:

    # s "[player_name], don't get me started about that, okay?"
    s "[player_name]、もうそれ以上やめて。わかった？"

# game/day1.rpy:2152
translate japanese street_sima_71e15efb:

    # p "Did I say something wrong?"
    p "なんか嫌なことでも言った？"

# game/day1.rpy:2153
translate japanese street_sima_83642a5f:

    # s "No, it's just... well, that's a different story. Maybe I'll tell you later."
    s "違うけど…その話は別。また今度でも話すかも"

# game/day1.rpy:2157
translate japanese street_sima_2a684149:

    # "I always thought Sima's been very popular throughout her life, but..."
    "シマ、ずっと人気者だと思ってたけどなんか…"

# game/day1.rpy:2158
translate japanese street_sima_fbce9f58:

    # "Somehow, her words make me less confident about it."
    "そんな気じゃなくなっていた"

# game/day1.rpy:2160
translate japanese street_sima_c27e29e1:

    # s "Anyway, real friends are so rare that I'm unlikely to find them in the streets."
    s "まぁ、とりあえず本当の友達は、そんな道端でできるもんじゃないから"

# game/day1.rpy:2162
translate japanese street_sima_644ce77b:

    # p "It's worth the try, I think, because a friend can stay with your forever."
    p "やってみないと。だって友達は一生ものだよ"

# game/day1.rpy:2164
translate japanese street_sima_92190630:

    # s "I'm afraid my friendships don't last, [player_name]..."
    s "友達が続かないのが怖いの[player_name]…"

# game/day1.rpy:2166
translate japanese street_sima_7501552e:

    # p "What happens?"
    p "何がおきるの？"

# game/day1.rpy:2168
translate japanese street_sima_a00fa564:

    # s "I tend to think that people are good friends while you're even."
    s "人って、同じ同士ほど仲良くできると思うんだよねー"

# game/day1.rpy:2170
translate japanese street_sima_26f496f8:

    # s "However, as soon as you start doing better..."
    s "でも、その人より良くやり始めると…"

# game/day1.rpy:2172
translate japanese street_sima_41a9b159:

    # s "They think you're out of their league, and become increasingly distant."
    s "その仲良しだと思った人が、私とは格が違うって思い込んで、すごく距離を取り始めるの"

# game/day1.rpy:2174
translate japanese street_sima_769c1db5:

    # s "Don't know whether they're envious or just feeling uncomfortable."
    s "ただ居心地悪いのか、羨ましいのかがわからなくて"

# game/day1.rpy:2176
translate japanese street_sima_b734ce51:

    # p "I think I know what you're talking about..."
    p "分かる気がする"

# game/day1.rpy:2178
translate japanese street_sima_27da5b9a:

    # s "But what you probably don't know is that I come from a wealthy, noble family."
    s "でも、あたなが知らないのは、私は結構裕福な家庭からくるの"

# game/day1.rpy:2180
translate japanese street_sima_5832fbfd:

    # s "Trust me, it makes things even worse."
    s "だから、なおさらひどいの。信じて"

# game/day1.rpy:2182
translate japanese street_sima_ceade429:

    # p "Something tells me you'd never make a big deal out of it."
    p "このこと大げさにしたことないでしょ？"

# game/day1.rpy:2184
translate japanese street_sima_168d647e:

    # s "Exactly! Still, my social status alone is enough for people to alienate me."
    s "もちろん！でも、社会的地位が高いだけで人に遠ざけられるの"

# game/day1.rpy:2186
translate japanese street_sima_62b24462:

    # s "Money ruins friendships."
    s "お金は友情関係を台無しにしちゃう"

# game/day1.rpy:2188
translate japanese street_sima_1f1cc9f0:

    # s "What's even worse, \"friends\" often become leaches."
    s "もっとひどいのが、その友達だと思った人たちがお金目的でまつわってくるの"

# game/day1.rpy:2190
translate japanese street_sima_334e4532:

    # s "When I'm not able to help them, they're all like..."
    s "私が手伝えないとき、彼らは…"

# game/day1.rpy:2192
